00:40:34.655 --> 00:40:37.408
Oh, man. Down for the count.

423
00:40:37.950 --> 00:40:39.952
Gentlemen.

424
00:40:40.161 --> 00:40:42.496
I understand there's been an incident.

425
00:40:42.705 --> 00:40:45.082
