454
00:43:11.603 --> 00:43:13.731
- Jordan, there is no Island! Come on!
- No.

455
00:43:15.524 --> 00:43:18.110
I got Six Echo in Female Tower,
floor 32.

456
00:43:18.277 --> 00:43:20.696
- He's got a female product in tow.
