457
00:43:20.904 --> 00:43:23.198
Get out of the way! Watch out.

458
00:43:23.407 --> 00:43:25.075
Move! Move!

459
00:43:25.284 --> 00:43:27.244
Out of the way. Get out. Now.

460
00:43:28.120 --> 00:43:29.163
Just trust me.

